lconf 0.0.2
* changed storage to use YAML, all kinds of complex objects can now be stored
in options.
* fixed dozens of bugs in the code, cleaned many things up
* changed the API in many ways
* now uses rubygems
* added rdoc documentation
* added test suite
* a lot more, maybe this should have been 0.1.0
lconf 0.0.1b
* Made writes atomic, fixed a number of issues, added and updated
documentation 
lconf 0.0.1a 
* Small patch to change the order of searched paths
lconf 0.0.1
* First released version
